                        "The Resort offers a wide variety of cuisine options at every turn, including cosmopolitan selection of Chinese, Western, Southeast Asian and Japanese delicacies. Our imaginative chefs create mouth-watering food items inspired by classic Disney Characters, such as the Mickey Waffles, Stitch and Lotso Sherbet Bars and more.",
